OL,7,FIn the first six months of this year,
OL,8,Fvisas granted to dependants of
OL,9,Foverseas students tumbled by 81% to
OL,10,F11,675 compared to the same period in
OL,11,F2023.
OL,13,FIt follows plans announced in May 2023
OL,14,Fby the Conservative government to
OL,15,Fblock international sponsored students
OL,16,Ffrom bringing dependants with them to
OL,17,Fthe UK.
OL,19,FThe number of health and care worker
OL,20,Fvisas granted was also 26% lower
OL,21,Fcompared to the same period last year.
