OL,7,FThis comes after the previous
OL,8,Fgovernment introduced changes in
OL,9,FMarch, which restricted overseas care
OL,10,Fworkers from bringing relatives with
OL,11,Fthem to the UK.
OL,13,FThe latest Home Office figures show
OL,14,Fthe number of NHS and social care
OL,15,Fvisas granted in the year to June 2024
OL,16,Fwas down 26% on the previous year.
OL,18,FThe statistics have also shown a four-
OL,19,Ffold increase in the number of
OL,20,Fdecisions being made on all asylum
OL,21,Fclaims between June 2023 and June 2024.
