OL,7,FAsylum backlog creeps up again
OL,9,FThe data released shows the UK's
OL,10,Fasylum processing backlog dropped by
OL,11,Falmost a third in a year, but started
OL,12,Fcreeping back up again in the spring
OL,13,Fof 2024.
OL,15,FA total of 118,882 people were waiting
OL,16,Ffor an initial decision on an asylum
OL,17,Fapplication in the UK at the end of
OL,18,FJune 2024, down by 32% from 175,457 at
OL,19,Fthe end of June 2023.
