OL,7,FBut the latest total has risen
OL,8,Fslightly from the 118,329 waiting to
OL,9,Fbe dealt with at the end of March this
OL,10,Fyear, indicating a rise in the last
OL,11,Fthree months up until June 2024.
OL,13,FMarley Morris, from the Institute for
OL,14,FPublic Policy Research (IPPR),
OL,15,Fbelieves the previous government's
