OL,7,FAccording to the Home Office
OL,8,Fstatistics, over 97,000 applied for
OL,9,Fasylum in the UK between June 2023 and
OL,10,FJune 2024 - a drop of 8% compared to
OL,11,Fthe previous year, which the
OL,12,Fdepartment said is due to a decrease
OL,13,Fin claims from Albanian small boat
OL,14,Farrivals.
