OL,8,Fsecretary's announcement of new
OL,9,Fmeasures to tackle illegal
OL,10,Fimmigration, including hiring more
OL,11,Fspecialist officers to dismantle
OL,12,Fsmuggling gangs, and increasing
OL,13,Fdeportation flights.
